1. ( PERFECTION IS THE FIRST PILLAR OF LIFE )
    you can not find water by shallow digging in 100 places,
    but you will definitely find water by continuous digging at one place.

2. ( PATIENCE IS THE SECOND PILLAR OF LIFE )
    fruits will come at their time no matter you waters the plant with 100 tanks.

3. ( SILENCE IS THE THIRD PILLAR OF LIFE )
    the power of silence is unfathomable

4. ( ACCEPTANCE IS THE FOURTH PILLAR OF LIFE )
    accept everything that comes in life whether happiness or sadness.

